                        Saving the game is not possible, so do not close the window.
                        Requires Java 8.
                    `
            game-item sitarhero
                name sitar hero
                img sitarhero.png
                link jar://sitarhero
                desc Guitar-hero style 3-song music game using MIDI Sitar. Made with Java for SFHS CS. 2016.
                alt-links https://github.com/anuvgupta/sitarhero
                controls
                    `
                        Download jar file and double click to open. Alternatively, run in terminal/command prompt: `java -jar sitarhero.jar`.
                        Use ASDFGH as six sitar strings/keyboard notes from left to right. Hit the notes when they enter the black box.
                        Saving the game is not possible, so do not close the window.
                        Requires Java 8.
                    `
            game-item worldcup
                name world cup
                img worldcup.png
                link jar://worldcup
                desc Simulation of "world cup" soccer practice minigame. Made with Java for SFHS CS. 2016.
                alt-links https://github.com/chern/JWorldCup
                controls
                    `
                        Download jar file and double click to open. Alternatively, to see log output, run in terminal/command prompt: `java -jar worldcup.jar`.
                        Adjust speed and # players with control panel. Game can be saved to/loaded from a file "worldcup.csv" in same folder as "worldcup.jar".
                        Requires Java 8.
                    `
            game-item spaceinvaders
                name space invaders
                img spaceinvaders.png
                link jar://spaceinvaders
                desc Rudimentary space-invaders-style minigame. Made with Java for ID Tech @ Stanford. 2012.
                alt-links https://github.com/anuvgupta/spaceinvaders
                controls
                    `
                        Download jar file and double click to open. Alternatively, to see log output, run in terminal/command prompt: `java -jar spaceinvaders.jar`.
                        Use left/right arrow keys to move and space to shoot. Move the main window to the side to see the scores/lives window.
                        Requires Java 8.
                    `
            game-item catchapples
                name catch the apples
                img catchapples.png
                link jar://catchapples
                desc Rudimentary item-catching minigame. Made with Java for ID Tech @ Stanford. 2012.
                alt-links https://github.com/anuvgupta/catchapples
                controls
                    `
                        Download jar file and double click to open. Alternatively, to see log output, run in terminal/command prompt: `java -jar catchapples.jar`.
                        Use left/right arrow keys to move and collect apples. Requires Java 8.
                    `
